This game contains the following elements:
Mild Violence：Fights without gore or blood;
Realistic Violence：Blood(self-harm through wrist-cutting);violent acts(physical assault, kidnapping), bodily injury  (suggestive cinematography, non-hemorrhagic interrogation);
Suicide: Storylines involving attempted suicide (e.g., failed jumping from heights, simulated death from wrist-cutting);
Crime：emotional fraud (Honey Trap), physical assault, and kidnapping;
Language：Mild profanity, swearing, cursing;
Nudity Or Sexual Content：Revealing outfits (swimsuits,bikinis), Veiled nudity, non-explicit sexual content (intense kissing, bed scenes), some nudity（clothes falling off during intimacy）;
Legal drugs: heavy drinking;
Adult venues: bars, massage parlors.
